text: Alicia Roanne Witt (born August 21 1975) is an American singer, model and actor. She was in the movie Citizen Ruth (1996). She was born in Worcester, Massachusetts. She acted on television shows Ally McBeal and The Sopranos. == References == Category:Actors from Massachusetts Category:American television actors Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:People from Worcester, Massachusetts
